column1: # Appendix 1 of Holdaway et al. 2016 Design of New Zealand's grid -based plot network (Landcare Research contract report)
# Static Master Data for national 8km plot grid
# Columns F-K = ideal gird-based plot location, in NZTM, NZMG and WGS84
# Columns B & C = ideal randomised year of measurement for a 5 year measurement cycle for all plots
# Columns D & E = ideal randomised year of measurement for a 10 year measurement cycle for all plots
# Column L = regional boundaries based on the New Zealand 2016 12 mile high definition spatial layer, downloaded from Statistics New Zealand on 14 April 2016
